name: The First Responders
overview: A police station and a fire station adjoining each other cooperate in combating crime and fire in the most brutal and tragic cases.

seasons.name: The Police Station Next to the Fire Station
seasons.overview: Police combat crime and firefighters combat fire. The first responders cooperate in crises.

seasons.name: The Police Station Next to the Fire Station and the National Forensic Service
seasons.overview: Firefighters fighting fires, police catching criminals, and National Forensic Service finding evidences!  The upgrade cooperation against unprecedented and never happen before cases begins!

tagline: A special task force made up of the finest police officers and firefighters

episodes.name: Code Zero
episodes.overview: On his first day, Detective Jin Ho-gae works jointly with firefighters to resolve a kidnapping case.

episodes.name: Code Two
episodes.overview: The first responders try to stop a suicide attempt, but the case turns out to be more complicated.

episodes.name: CODE YELLOW
episodes.overview: Ho-gae's house is said to be haunted. He and Do-jin try to solve the mystery that lies in the ashes.

episodes.name: Code V30.
episodes.overview: A driver is arrested after a hit-and-run accident of a child. A shocking truth awaits.

episodes.name: CODE BLACK
episodes.overview: Ho-gae starts an undercover operation. He must stop a crisis that may result in mass casualties.

episodes.name: CODE RED
episodes.overview: An unidentified body is found at the scene of a fire. An unlikely person is held as a suspect.

episodes.name: CODE BLUE
episodes.overview: Ho-gae identifies a new suspect, while the case becomes evermore ensnared in mystery.

episodes.name: CODE CLEAR
episodes.overview: Ho-gae reinvestigates a murder case and gets help from Song Seol and Yoon Hong.

episodes.name: CODE PINK
episodes.overview: Firefighters rush to save a teenage girl attempting suicide. Police find a body of a newborn baby.

episodes.name: CODE AMBER
episodes.overview: The first responders search for the father of the stillborn child. They then meet a strange patient.

episodes.name: CODE 1
episodes.overview: Ho-gae misses Hyun-seo by a second. He and Seol pursue the evasive kidnapper.

episodes.name: CODE.F63.1
episodes.overview: A series of fire incidents occur. Do-jin suspects a chain arson and goes to see Ho-gae.

1.name: The Police Station Next to the Fire Station
1.overview: Police combat crime and firefighters combat fire. The first responders cooperate in crises.

episodes.name: Code Orange
episodes.overview: A bound corpse emerges following a serial arson. The first responders to unite in the investigation.

episodes.name: Code B
episodes.overview: Two fires break out in different locations. The first responders find themselves in a crisis.

episodes.name: Code R98
episodes.overview: The first responders and the NFS cooperate to uncover clues to the serial arsonist.

episodes.name: Code Grey
episodes.overview: The arsonist's final plan gets revealed. Can Ho-gae save everyone from danger and catch the criminal?

episodes.name: Lapport Building
episodes.overview: When a murder occurs at Myeong-pil's villa, Ho-gae leaves his post and joins the case. Kang Do-ha joins the National Forensic Service.

episodes.name: Salami Tactics
episodes.overview: Do-ha concludes that the death at the villa was an accident, but Ho-gae continues his investigation. Do-ha uncovers the dark side of the neighbours.

episodes.name: Hot Zone
episodes.overview: An unidentified body is found after a brawl at a junkyard. A crisis arises during the autopsy.

episodes.name: Code Green
episodes.overview: Criminals plan to endanger the NFS building. Can the team safeguard the place?

episodes.name: Code Purple
episodes.overview: The police and fire department respond to an urgent call about a horrifying incident regarding organ extractions.

episodes.name: Trust Fall
episodes.overview: Ho-gae delves into the investigation of Ma Joong-do's murder and reopens a past murder case and prison escape.

episodes.name: Overkill
episodes.overview: Ho-gae vanishes after a caravan explosion. Amidst the chaos, a showdown is drawing near.

episodes.name: Dying Message
episodes.overview: Supported by the NFS, the first responders confront the sinister mastermind in a decisive showdown.
